Class EventModel

java.lang.Object
com.example.single_lottery.EventModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class EventModel extends Object implements Serializable
Model class representing a lottery event. Stores event details including timing, capacity and registration information. Used for Firestore data mapping.
Version:
1.0
Author:
[Aaron kim], [Gabriel Bautista]
